# Implementation Guide - Socialaize Landing Page

*Source: Web Research Report + Competitive Analysis*
*Date: October 1, 2025*

This guide provides complete code examples and step-by-step implementation for the Socialaize landing page redesign.

---

## Complete Design System Setup

